{
  "stem": "9777.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She didn't know anything about Jewishness.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she comes from Jewish background.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had bleached blond hair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It still was growing out, whatever she had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was-- it was-- looked like she was blond to begin with.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she helped herself a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were making fun of her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were chopping her hair off in the most funniest way, you know, like-- not like they're giving a haircut, like making a rag doll out of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They sort of were chopping her hair off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What kind of an actor-- what kind of an art she know how to do?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If she said that she was a sculptor or a painter, they were laughing at her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they're making, really, a, a scapegoat out of her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People who had the special talents, like, ones that decide that they're going to make a show for us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're going to do the show ourselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're looking for volunteers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have too big hand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No, you have too big feet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They are making, you know, up extremely unpleasant remarks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the people were very vulnerable, all of us, account of we were cold and hungry and without parents, without hope, without any kind of a backbone.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, no, this, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this was the only attitude you could take.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whatever gonna be, gonna be.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only thing I realized something was wrong-- for three weeks, we didn't get not a drop of food or a drink of water.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got as bold as went outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a reservoir next to our barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we tried to tie a strings from whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember from what we made the strings.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
